# Nature's Infusions — Static E‑Store

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Privacy First](https://img.shields.io/badge/privacy-first-green.svg)](privacy.txt)

## Description

A small, privacy‑first static storefront for Nature's Infusions. Built with plain HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript. No build step. Focus on accessibility, semantic HTML, and a conservative, reviewable workflow.

## Technology Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- No build tools, no frameworks

## Architecture

- Static site, single-page structure
- Pages in `/pages/` and `/pages/store/`
- Assets in `/assets/css/`, `/assets/js/`, `/assets/img/`
- Product data in JSON under `/assets/js/data/`
- Service worker for offline/PWA support
- Web Workers for off-main-thread tasks (see `docs/WORKERS.md`)

## Features

- Accessibility-first design
- Privacy-first (no analytics, no trackers)
- Progressive Web App (PWA) with offline support
- Semantic HTML5 structure
- Machine-readable product data
- Simple, reversible workflow

