## Getting Started

Serve the site from a local static server (e.g., Python's http.server) to test service worker registration:

```sh
python -m http.server 8000
```

Test offline and 404 pages on localhost.

> For local development using the same Apache httpd setup as production, see `.vscode/tasks.md` for VS Code task usage (start/stop httpd, wait-for-port helper) and use the **Launch Chrome** debug configuration to start Apache and attach the debugger.

