## Contributing

- Keep changes small and reversible.
- Edit files directly under repo root, `pages/`, `pages/store/`, `assets/css/partials/`, `assets/js/data/`, `assets/js/modules/`.
- Add new assets only under `assets/` and reference them relatively.
- See [Copilot instructions](.github/copilot-instructions.md) and [Contribution prompts](.github/prompts/refactor-html.prompt.md).

